graph LR
    Input([HDFS Input Data]) -->|MRInput| V1[Vertex 1: Tokenizer Map]
    
    subgraph "Tez DAG Engine"
        V1 -->|Scatter-Gather Edge - Partitioner & Sort| V2[Vertex 2: Aggregation Reduce]
        V2 -->|One-to-One Edge - In-Memory Pipeline| V3[Vertex 3: Formatting & Filter Map]
    end

    V3 -->|MROutput| Output([HDFS Output Data])
    
    style V1 fill:#2c3e50,stroke:#fff,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style V2 fill:#3498db,stroke:#fff,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style V3 fill:#27ae60,stroke:#fff,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
